// This file will be written to by the global error handler in production.
// It will log fatal errors that cause WSOD for later review.

// Usage: The error overlay in index.html will append errors here.
// You can download or inspect this file after a WSOD event.

// Format: Each error is appended as a JSON object, one per line.

// Example entry:
// { "timestamp": "2026-04-29T12:34:56Z", "type": "error", "message": "Uncaught ReferenceError: x is not defined", "stack": "...stack trace...", "url": "...", "userAgent": "..." }
